title: Developing Good Habits | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Developing Good Habits | Joel Osteen
description:
Your habits have the power to determine your future. If you want to transform your life, start by transforming your everyday habits. When you commit to change for the better, God will take you further than you’ve ever dreamed. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
